{"tid":2003913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"再多萬人感染武肺 俄國三醫護離奇墮樓","createTime":"2020-05-06T06:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T06:58:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"34a7e80ca4320cc27aa9fb446530ef4560e95cc0","tid":2003913,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:21:13.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200506/OMIKBIPWWIHVERTYCSYHT6H4SI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200506%2FOMIKBIPWWIHVERTYCSYHT6H4SI%2F&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=ee21f13d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200506%2FOMIKBIPWWIHVERTYCSYHT6H4SI%2F&h=b7d4f485\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200506/OMIKBIPWWIHVERTYCSYHT6H4SI/</a><br />\n<br />\n再多萬人感染武肺<br />\n俄國三醫護離奇墮樓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200506/large/1588694553_adae.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200506%2Flarge%2F1588694553_adae.gif&h=01217fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俄羅斯昨日再多逾1萬人確診感染武漢肺炎，疫情嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯昨日再多逾1萬人確診感染武漢肺炎，在疫情嚴峻下，過去兩周先後有三名前線醫護人員從醫院窗戶離奇墮樓，造成兩死1傷，令外界關注當地醫護人員壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾投訴中招仍要當值<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：疫情回落打救經濟 澳紐商重開旅遊路線<br />\n<br />\n沃羅湼日市救護車醫生舒列波夫（Alexander Shulepov）上月22日確診武肺，同日他跟同僚科夏金在網上發。。。。。。。。。上月30日最後一次跟舒列波夫說話，當時對方在深切治療部，感覺不錯，準備出院，故此無法解釋他會墮樓。<br />\n<br />\n另外，西伯利亞醫院醫生主管湼波姆尼亞希（Elena Nepomnyashchaya），跟地區衞生部官員開會期間。。。。。。。。。。。管列別杰娃（Natalya Lebedeva）墮樓身亡，她所屬的醫院隸屬聯邦生物醫學局，指她疑感染武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡"},{"pid":"b90cb80140f1a1091d0d3498f90d0dafb00bdbfe","tid":2003913,"uid":15815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"共產黨呢招七傷拳的確前無古人<br />\n美蘇冷戰咁耐都未試過一野整瓜咁多鬼佬鬼婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24eb34603791969ce5096bffe7bbcfc7eca9b1c","tid":2003913,"uid":54303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b90cb80140f1a1091d0d3498f90d0dafb00bdbfe","tid":2003913,"uid":15815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"共產黨呢招七傷拳的確前無古人<br />\n美蘇冷戰咁耐都未試過一野整瓜咁多鬼佬鬼婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:52:55.000Z","msg":"支那人闖大禍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd0648800eb1a01ed19560bf51108a836cd100b","tid":2003913,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b90cb80140f1a1091d0d3498f90d0dafb00bdbfe","tid":2003913,"uid":15815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"共產黨呢招七傷拳的確前無古人<br />\n美蘇冷戰咁耐都未試過一野整瓜咁多鬼佬鬼婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"仲要搞撚死埋普京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}